  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if the adherence to screening in first grade
      relatives of patients with CCR is higher than optical colonoscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the adherence and effectiveness of colon capsule
      endoscopy (CCE-2) versus conventional colonoscopy to screen first-degree relatives of
      patients with colorectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
